Cervantes' portrait based on José del Castillo´s design for Madrid: Ibarra, 1780 (copied and modified in later editions).The ornamental frame includes several scenes (after Tony Johannot, Paris: Dubochet, 1836-37) about Cervantes' life: a) Lepanto battle; b) Cervantes holdingDon Quixote; c) Readers ofDon Quixote; d) Cervantes writing his prologue with a friend; f) Cervantes and Lope de Rueda.
